Package: rpptx
Type: Package
Title: Edit PowerPoint Documents In R
Version: 0.1.1.0
Author: Justin Kracht
Maintainer: Justin Kracht <justin.kracht@genmills.com>
Description: Edit a PowerPoint template document by replacing images and text with new images and
    text, preserving size (images) or formatting (text). This is useful for creating many versions
    of a template presentation. E.g., for creating personalized decks of engagement survey
    results for each member of the Senior Leadership Team.
